\begin_layout Subsection
To decide, strategize, and design
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
When you've gotta make a decision (no matter what you do), it's helpful
 to build or structure information in a way to make better decisions.
 You'll learn about things like decision trees and game theory models, to
 help make better decisions and to strategize better.
 Moreover, at the very end of class (notes), we'll talk about design issues.
 One can use models to design things like institutions, policies etc.
 So, models just make people better at making choices and taking actions.
\end_layout

